page.title: 17AROUND AND ABOUT LYNEHAM
page.content: I WENT TO NEW ZEALAND IN MISS DOYLE'S CAR.I STROKED A CAT I COUNTED 53 HOUSES IN NEW ZEALAND AND GOAT_ACRE. COLIN LANG 6YRS. IN NEW ZEALAND WE SAW A CHICKEN FARM.THEY SELL FRESH EGGS WE SAW PUPPIES FOR SALE AND THEY WERE BARKING. TANYA BELL 6YRS. WE WENT TO TOCKENHAM TRIANGLE AND STOPPED AT A POND.WE SAW FISH AND BULLRUSHES.WE PICKED DEAD NETTLE AND BUTTERCUPS AND SOME COW PARSLEY. VICKY BURCHEL 6YRS. MRS O'SULLIVAN TOOK US TO BLUE BELL WOOD THE BLUE BELLS WERE LOVELY VICTORIA HAWKINS 5YRS.
